column5: The wife and I had a date last night we both got slimed here is a tease

Good thing this is a fishing site and we get the slang!  Nice Mike!

No socks the wife would not be seen with me if I had them on thanks all it was a great night  Chris the new one is sitting on the outer desk

Can't beat a date like that!
